  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Are you ready to start collecting new and adorable creatures?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⭐ <strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>+30</strong> different creatures</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4</strong> different seasons</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Day and night cycle:</strong> Day lasts 2 minutes, and night lasts 10 seconds (Cinematic)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capture creatures by dragging them with the <strong>click</strong> and bringing them inside the farm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic:</strong> You control everything with your <strong>mouse</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visitors will <strong>react</strong> every time they see a creature</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛑 <strong>STOP</strong> <i>the unruly creatures</i><br>📢 <strong>Bring order to your ranch!</strong> Click on the <strong>rowdy creatures</strong> so they <strong>stop fighting.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/3b80fd2088a90adc5767d24a4efe8db8.poster.avif?t=1749008017\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/3b80fd2088a90adc5767d24a4efe8db8.webm?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/3b80fd2088a90adc5767d24a4efe8db8.mp4?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❗ <strong>Don't let them escape!</strong><br>🐾 If a creature is <strong>loose</strong>, <strong>visitors panic.</strong> <i>Capture it before it causes a disaster!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/ca22f7d141471c87f8743df2e31fd15d.poster.avif?t=1749008017\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/ca22f7d141471c87f8743df2e31fd15d.webm?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/ca22f7d141471c87f8743df2e31fd15d.mp4?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✋ <strong>TAKE CONTROL!</strong><br>🐷 Grab a creature <strong>in time</strong> <strong>before it becomes a feast!</strong> Hold the <i>click</i> to free the visitor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/0c664ccb523b1904d03edd3de695b376.poster.avif?t=1749008017\" width=480 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/0c664ccb523b1904d03edd3de695b376.webm?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3560280/extras/0c664ccb523b1904d03edd3de695b376.mp4?t=1749008017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
